Package com.gsm.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuditableEntity
    An abstract base class for entities that require auditing information.
    BOMTemplate
    Represents the BOM (Bill of Materials) Template entity.
    BOMTemplateDetail
    Represents a single line item within a BOMTemplate.
    Customer
    Represents a customer entity in the database.
    Fabric
    Represents the core Fabric entity.
    FabricColor
    Represents a specific color variant of a Fabric.
    MaterialGroup
    Represents a group for raw materials, used for classification.
    OrderBOM
    Represents the header of a Bill of Materials (BOM) for a specific Sale Order.
    OrderBOMDetail
    Represents a single line item (a material) within an OrderBOM.
    Product
    Represents the core Product entity in the system.
    ProductCategory
    Represents a category for products (e.g., T-Shirt, Jacket).
    ProductionOutput
    Represents a single production output record.
    ProductVariant
    Represents a specific variant of a Product.
    PurchaseOrder
    Represents the core Purchase Order (PO) entity.
    PurchaseOrderDetail
    Represents a single line item within a PurchaseOrder.
    SaleOrder
    Represents the core Sale Order entity, acting as the header for a customer's order.
    SaleOrderDetail
    Represents a single line item within a SaleOrder.
    Supplier
    Represents a supplier of raw materials.
    Trim  
    TrimVariant
    Represents a specific variant of a trim (e.g., a button in a specific color and size).
    Unit
    Represents a unit of measure (e.g., PCS, YDS, MTR).
    User
    Represents a user of the application.
